description:
Danny talks about the new Hulu Housewives documentary about Bamboozle J and Tommy 2T, then recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured a socially-distant dinner, ear drops in the eyes, and a train-style rowboat? On The Real Housewives of New York. the group paints a naked man, has some of Garth's curry, and lots more!


RHONY Recap: 27:15ish
